640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:00:05.000Z","msg":"今次真係擺明俾你睇配合藍店犯罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30da0baf56e198a4ca67c9c00e8c958a316a4a9","tid":2011191,"uid":13518,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:00:59.000Z","msg":"啲老一輩仲用緊十幾廿年前既諗法<br />\n諗住做十幾廿年 公司會重情重義 所謂無功都有勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好on9"},{"pid":"5c73e88daa1604463bde3b7864c3aae4d56b01aa","tid":2011191,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:02:05.000Z","msg":"打份閪工 <br />\n打到自己有股份咁"},{"pid":"0de0e3d8814b2ca806b10b92d1d390800f91d864","tid":2011191,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3e4c094858a3f7ea7d3e49cfa623dd50c7027b","tid":2011191,"uid":60744,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9e1865681ca92fca73053e864dfb6cfa2a2c3e5","tid":2011191,"uid":14494,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T23:24:19.000Z","msg":"呢鑊popo係藍絲谷扣晒分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:07:35.000Z","msg":"點會，藍絲唔燒到自己都只會覺得受害者抵死"},{"pid":"0a1a0c1553bc303142eaf2c8ff36fa0dba16abcd","tid":2011191,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b931cc3747f60052f912469253537240ee6ab11d","tid":2011191,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e30da0baf56e198a4ca67c9c00e8c958a316a4a9","tid":2011191,"uid":13518,"like":3,"dislike":1,"sco