32e88b6","tid":2011191,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f48ef42883f145ff6b36f3904763ea01b617c1d4","tid":2011191,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e30da0baf56e198a4ca67c9c00e8c958a316a4a9","tid":2011191,"uid":13518,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:00:59.000Z","msg":"啲老一輩仲用緊十幾廿年前既諗法<br />\n諗住做十幾廿年 公司會重情重義 所謂無功都有勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好on9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T01:13:33.000Z","msg":"同埋行得正企得正點解怕警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T01:54:19.000Z","msg":"其實好多藍絲都係比呢啲野灌輸左入腦<br />\n因為佢地在世幾廿年 經歷緊都係安穩既生活<br />\n幾廿年警察真係秉公辦理 呢啲習慣諗法真係一時間好難改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}